content: I'm thinking of staying in Europe for around 7-10 days. I've also considered visiting Barcelona or Amsterdam, but I'm not sure yet. I'll have to do some more research and see what each city has to offer. But I definitely want to spend a few days in Paris and try to see the Eiffel Tower and the Louvre. And in Rome, I want to visit the Colosseum and try some authentic Italian food.
